#~ "ilmuvast menüüst käsk <guimenuitem>Sulge vaade</guimenuitem>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you use &konqueror; tabs, you can drag and drop between tabs by "
#~ "dragging the file to the tab label, without letting go yet. The "
#~ "destination tab will pop to the front, allowing you to continue dragging "
#~ "and then to drop the file."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui kasutad &konqueror;is kaarte, võid lohistada ka kaartide vahel, "
