#~ msgid ""
#~ "Allows you to validate your &CSS; style sheet that is embedded in an "
#~ "&HTML; or &XHTML; document. Having valid &CSS; is critical to ensuring "
#~ "that your web site maintains a consistent look regardless of the browser "
